The table is structured to support financial and usage reporting, for auditing, billing reconciliation, and customer account management purposes.

Analyzing energy consumption patterns and demand usage for operational insights.
Auditing and reconciling billed amounts against actual usage to ensure accuracy.
Supporting customer service operations by providing detailed account and billing information.
